Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.55,0:00:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄昏降临
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.32,0:00:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算黑暗吞噬一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.97,0:00:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.85,0:00:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那持续闪烁的星屑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.37,0:00:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像朝阳那般
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.94,0:00:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻燃烧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.70,0:01:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是认真的吗 父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.20,0:01:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲现在被杀手盯上了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.83,0:01:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,采购商品交给别人不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.05,0:01:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,商品一定要自己经手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.17,0:02:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我一贯的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.63,0:02:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在城镇里还好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.66,0:02:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开城镇的话就比较危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.63,0:02:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们当然也要作为护卫一同前往
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.56,0:02:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是契约的一环
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.74,0:02:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么可抱怨的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.16,0:02:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直说契约 契约的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.18,0:02:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.64,0:02:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.75,0:02:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧泽鲁 拜托你准备一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.34,0:02:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.92,0:02:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.18,0:02:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这简直和说“请来袭击我”没两样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.24,0:02:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.27,0:02:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.22,0:02:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他无法再忍受这种随时会被袭击的生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.86,0:02:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.51,0:02:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意制造容易被袭击的机会 然后一口气做个了结
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.38,0:02:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这样的话 自己也就陷入危险之中了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.29,0:03:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有比自己还优先的目标在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.99,0:03:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.74,0:03:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 莉娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.75,0:03:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.11,0:03:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明如此 为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.94,0:03:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想再这样陪他们玩下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.29,0:03:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人盯上不说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.52,0:03:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那对父子在暗地里说三道四我可受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.39,0:03:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 莉娜被干掉了的话 不就轮到他了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.35,0:03:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在想 那时候还有你们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.64,0:03:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.81,0:03:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一我被祖玛干掉了 你们会怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.58,0:03:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办的话…首先要举行葬礼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.03,0:03:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不愿意这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.48,0:03:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从恐怖动漫的铁则来看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.84,0:03:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了以防莉娜复活
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.81,0:03:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要请人来驱邪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.84,0:03:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后用大石头压住坟墓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.74,0:03:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再用强效的符咒进行严密的封印
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.15,0:03:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我是什么恶灵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.26,0:03:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是没人情啊 你们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.65,0:04:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想过为我报仇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.70,0:04:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不怎么想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.26,0:04:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一我被干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.25,0:04:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便你们不愿意 也要去拉多库身边守护
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.22,0:04:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待祖玛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.30,0:04:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以那个大叔就觉得自己的危险会减少吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.35,0:04:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.98,0:04:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我负责保护拉多库 和他们坐一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.82,0:04:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们就坐那边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.97,0:04:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 要抱怨和拉多库说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.27,0:04:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.72,0:04:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想途中被人说三道四
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.26,0:04:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.44,0:04:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就坐这辆破马车悠闲地前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.28,0:04:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 我忘了这一出了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.71,0:04:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.99,0:04:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.92,0:04:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 马上就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.62,0:04:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.83,0:05:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说了都决定好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.08,0:05:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是来阻止你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.12,0:05:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.81,0:05:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.39,0:05:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我迟早要继承父亲的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.71,0:05:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想跟着父亲学习
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.41,0:05:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.83,0:05:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样父亲就无话可说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.86,0:05:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你的便
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.62,0:05:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说三道四的人又多了一个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.55,0:05:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边反倒很轻松…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.78,0:05:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.45,0:05:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别拉我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.82,0:05:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uncover 暴露的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.65,0:05:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别唱这歌了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.33,0:06:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都不敢想象会这样和父亲一同出行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.37,0:06:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是父子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.03,0:06:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很久没和其他人一同出行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲总是独来独往啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.43,0:06:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气…气氛好沉重
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.99,0:06:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停在这里合适吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.15,0:06:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马也需要休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.30,0:06:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我们去护卫拉多库
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.93,0:06:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周边就拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.70,0:07:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来如此眺望风景 也是旅行的乐趣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.64,0:07:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被杀手盯上了还有这样的心情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.36,0:07:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲被杀手盯上 到底为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.80,0:07:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生意做大了 总会招些意想不到的怨恨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.77,0:07:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲的死也是因为这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.63,0:07:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.76,0:07:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.84,0:07:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是跟你说明你母亲死因的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.16,0:07:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还是我的父亲 你祖父当家时的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.21,0:07:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲是个非常成功的商人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.67,0:08:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然暗地里使过不少手段
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.05,0:08:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此招来了怨恨和嫉妒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.02,0:08:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是 我和你的母亲被盯上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.13,0:08:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在商谈的途中被盗贼袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.48,0:08:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒来时 发现被关在了不知是何处的地牢里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.62,0:08:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也因为那时的伤…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.49,0:08:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在父亲答应支付赎金前的那段时间里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.48,0:08:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能看着你那再也不会动的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.85,0:08:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.65,0:08:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中一个盗贼说过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.23,0:09:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要恨就恨你的家庭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.26,0:09:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那岂不是有人雇佣了盗贼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.28,0:09:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲难道若无其事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.02,0:09:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲可是因为家族的事而被杀害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.13,0:09:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又能做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.73,0:09:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住盗贼 找出幕后主使吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.33,0:09:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这明显不切实际
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 就因为这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.78,0:09:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做生意经常会遇到此类事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.08,0:09:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想要继承这个家族的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.72,0:09:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.94,0:09:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会继承这些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.91,0:09:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.97,0:09:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想让我忘记杀母之仇去继承这个家族吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.77,0:09:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明什么都不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.65,0:09:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的确不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.04,0:09:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁能理解父亲的这种想法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也难怪那家伙会生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.13,0:09:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 波克塔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.27,0:09:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.05,0:09:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦 怎么说我们也是护卫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.75,0:09:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在周围的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.60,0:10:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多管闲事的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.75,0:10:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道不应该执着于复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.03,0:10:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 这样很多事就无法挥之而去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.01,0:10:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 即便复仇也未必能拯救谁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.70,0:10:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在也无法复仇了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.21,0:10:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些盗贼似乎数年前死于了某场战斗之中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.02,0:10:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那场发生在拥有神圣之树的城市塞拉格的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.07,0:10:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我也没有忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.45,0:10:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我也无法忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.00,0:10:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着爱人在自己的面前死去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.47,0:10:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉多库
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.96,0:10:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那股气息…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.32,0:10:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.51,0:10:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷萨恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.80,0:11:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要离开我的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.65,0:11:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.60,0:11:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.24,0:11:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷萨恶魔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.37,0:11:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.98,0:11:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.94,0:11:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等 拉多库
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.68,0:11:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰之矢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.34,0:11:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.07,0:11:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们去追拉多库
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.58,0:11:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.39,0:11:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.53,0:12:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在森林里视野非常不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.87,0:12:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔封界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.51,0:12:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.55,0:12:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔封界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.38,0:12:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼 疼 疼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.94,0:12:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.68,0:12:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.76,0:12:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.30,0:12:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你走了之后 雷萨恶魔就袭击而来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父…父亲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.69,0:12:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.12,0:12:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担心你 于是追了上来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.33,0:12:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.93,0:12:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不是父亲所雇佣的护卫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.69,0:12:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.03,0:12:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.37,0:12:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉多库老爷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.06,0:12:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.07,0:12:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.88,0:12:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.64,0:12:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.50,0:12:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了 看来客人们也到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.97,0:13:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.60,0:13:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封气结界咒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.88,0:13:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.25,0:13:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.27,0:13:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心点 这些家伙不管对手是谁都会袭击的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.33,0:13:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.31,0:13:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西一个个来倒不算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.13,0:13:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是居然有这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.64,0:13:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一个人先逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.96,0:13:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以 父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.34,0:13:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧泽鲁 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.85,0:13:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护阿贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.85,0:13:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 我的使命是侍奉拉多库老爷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开你是不可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.99,0:13:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就将两个人一起送到安全的地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.42,0:13:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有我们呢 况且你们在也会碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.27,0:13:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.76,0:13:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青魔烈弹波
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.32,0:13:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵王结魔弹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.71,0:13:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就结束了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.88,0:13:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上去追莉娜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.18,0:13:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.30,0:14:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时的魔族
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.63,0:14:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我俩受命来牵制你们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.09,0:14:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然不会仅此而已了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.65,0:14:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么比纠缠不休的家伙更讨厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.07,0:14:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好 阿贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.20,0:14:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直跑下去 直到安全为止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.97,0:14:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.79,0:14:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.34,0:14:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.23,0:14:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就全部收拾掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.43,0:14:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.22,0:14:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祖玛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.56,0:14:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出场有些晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.50,0:14:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火炎球
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.67,0:14:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个不问青红皂白的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.38,0:15:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿梅莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.88,0:15:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.85,0:15:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是没有自知之明
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.06,0:15:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能多陪我们玩下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.00,0:15:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虚灵瘴界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.07,0:15:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎之矢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.92,0:15:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.71,0:15:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振动弹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.11,0:16:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是老样子 很难缠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.83,0:16:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过已经了解他的身手了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.00,0:16:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并非敌不过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.39,0:16:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.93,0:16:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙为了达成目的 什么都会干的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定要做个了结
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.51,0:16:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不能再让你像蜥蜴一样 掉个尾巴就跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.43,0:16:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这双新手可不是为了逃跑而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.40,0:16:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是为了给背上饶痒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.15,0:16:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了打倒你们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.48,0:16:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此我弄到了冥王之壶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.52,0:16:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冥王之壶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.84,0:16:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用沉睡在其中的雷藏之力使我和魔族融合
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.01,0:16:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷藏之力 魔族…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.27,0:16:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.64,0:16:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.31,0:16:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来到此为止了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.25,0:16:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.42,0:16:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不到黄河心不死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.80,0:17:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿梅莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先把小姑娘大卸八块吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.90,0:17:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.52,0:17:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.23,0:17:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.26,0:17:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的魔族
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.83,0:17:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.07,0:17:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等遵守雷藏的契约前来帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.45,0:17:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区一个刺客居然…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.15,0:17:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.95,0:17:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我向雷藏索取的只是这双手的祭品
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.40,0:17:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不是指手画脚的手下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.79,0:17:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟把魔族吸入自己的体内
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.52,0:17:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.41,0:17:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为刺客…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.99,0:18:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 连作为人类的自尊都抛弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.06,0:18:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.93,0:18:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事去那个世界后再想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.23,0:18:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.27,0:18:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.42,0:18:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还有必须要去做的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.49,0:18:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高里 波克塔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.57,0:18:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙有那两个魔族的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.36,0:18:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.42,0:18:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.19,0:18:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.16,0:18:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.91,0:18:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了 父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.48,0:18:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.25,0:18:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 阿贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.50,0:18:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲 为什么非要如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.66,0:19:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父…父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.38,0:19:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管什么时候都不听父亲的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.85,0:19:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祖玛是拉多库吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.80,0:19:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.57,0:19:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.92,0:19:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.47,0:19:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.91,0:19:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 继续吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.91,0:19:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉多库 到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.91,0:19:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迄今为止都是在做戏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.86,0:19:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了我们 连阿贝尔也骗了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.40,0:19:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你怎么想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.45,0:19:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无可奉告
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.89,0:19:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.95,0:19:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神灭斩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.25,0:20:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.01,0:20:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.50,0:20:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我祖玛的生活方式
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.31,0:20:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人没资格评价
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.73,0:20:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很好吗 人各有志
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.19,0:20:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生活方式也一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.21,0:20:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰洛士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.88,0:20:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有死亡方式也是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.17,0:20:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊 打断了精彩的场景
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.98,0:21:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是不这样的话 冥王之壶就会一直在拉多库的手里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.42,0:21:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在等待夺取冥王之壶的机会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.77,0:21:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不能说我在暗中保护大家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.98,0:21:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.85,0:21:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个壶还不能交给你们魔族
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.61,0:21:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是雷藏大人的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.01,0:21:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果还打算抢的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.12,0:21:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就当场破坏它
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.58,0:21:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是认真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.29,0:21:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.84,0:21:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂且让你们保管吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.96,0:23:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于得到了冥王之壶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.54,0:23:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样所有的迷题都能解开了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.98,0:23:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的问题都能解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.62,0:23:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是这么觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.60,0:23:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 秀逗魔导士 进化-R
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.82,0:23:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Voice 壶中的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.00,0:23:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不看的话我会发飙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,

